            "Element": "Natural",
            "Name": "Gloompurge",
            "Desc": "Arcane creates a <@ba.key>Gloompurger Array</> that immediately deals <@ba.natur>Nature DMG</> to enemies within the area of effect (AOE).\nWhen hitting an enemy within the <@ba.key>Gloompurger Array</> with a Finisher or a <#ba.lastcombo>Final Strike</> performed by the controlled operator, the <@ba.key>Gloompurger Array</> unleashes a <@ba.key>Cluster Strike</> that deals Area DMG to the said enemy. This effect triggers up to 2 times.\nAfter triggering <@ba.key>Cluster Strike</> 2 times, the ultimate is switched to <@ba.key>Gloompurge Arcana</>.\n<@ba.key>Gloompurge Arcana</>: Deals <@ba.natur>Nature DMG</> to enemies within a large AOE.",
